{"thag2.20:0.1":"Theragatha 2.20 ","thag2.20:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.20:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag2.20:0.4":"Sirimattheragatha ","thag2.20:1.1":"“Pare ca nam pasamsanti, ","thag2.20:1.2":"atta ce asamahito; ","thag2.20:1.3":"Mogham pare pasamsanti, ","thag2.20:1.4":"atta hi asamahito. ","thag2.20:2.1":"Pare ca nam garahanti, ","thag2.20:2.2":"atta ce susamahito; ","thag2.20:2.3":"Mogham pare garahanti, ","thag2.20:2.4":"atta hi susamahito”ti. ","thag2.20:2.5":"… Sirima thero …. ","thag2.20:2.6":"vaggo dutiyo. ","thag2.20:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag2.20:3.1":"Cundo ca jotidaso ca, ","thag2.20:3.2":"thero herannakani ca; ","thag2.20:3.3":"Somamitto sabbamitto, ","thag2.20:3.4":"kalo tisso ca kimilo; ","thag2.20:3.5":"Nando ca sirima ceva, ","thag2.20:3.6":"dasa thera mahiddhikati. "}